name: Finders keypers (Charliewright)
description:
your in a maze but in a haze , Tigger's here to stop the craze  but before you get in a haze look out for Tigger's hints along the way.  

grab the keys for your ease and just maybe you will leave. 

try to escape the maze - if you can .. do you dare take up the challenge. 

Instructions:  To move  use WSAD and try to find keys to escape the maze , along the way you will meet a friend giving you hints on the directions you should go , use the minmap to help you around.
